Overview:
  Parse email messages and write out a network graph to parse with Gephi.

Assumptions:
- enron data has been imported into mongo as 'enron' db name

Software Requirements:
 - mongoengine
 - networkx
 - matplotlib
 - pygexf


Notes:
 matplotlib on OSX required
  brew install freetype
  brew install libpng
  pip install matplotlib

 pygexf required lxml
  pip install lxml



Sample output, on 2012 Macbook Pro.

